Installing Asterisks for the Raspberry pi

Go to: http://www.raspberry-asterisk.org/downloads/ and download the latest image of asterisk
FreePBX download Tutorial: http://wiki.freepbx.org/display/FD/Installing+FreePBX+Official+Distro
Learned how to set up Asterisk from : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Czd6yVRc4ac

Write to a 4mb SD card

username and pass(respectively): root and raspberry

To update Asterisk : 

raspbx-upgrade (takes a while)

